<li class="faq-item section">
<div class="topic collapsed at-action" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapsefaq_1025064563" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapsefaq_1025064563" data-tag="|TURBO HD CAMERA|" data-at-module="faq_list::click::How to Change PAL to NTSC for 3MP TVI Camera">How to Change PAL to NTSC for 3MP TVI Camera</div>
<div class="content-section collapse" id="collapsefaq_1025064563" data-parent="#faqAccordionfaq_container_copy">
    <div class="description hiknow-rte"><p>Connect the 3MP camera to DVR of HUHI models and you can operate locally or remotely</p>
</div>
    <ul class="assets-list">
        
        <li>
            <a class="asset at-action" href="https://www.tongfangbms.com/content/dam/tongfang/en/support/how-to/how-to-document/turbo-hd-cameras/How-to-Change-PAL-to-NTSC-for-3MP-TVI-Camera.pdf" style="background-image:url('https://www.tongfangbms.com/content/dam/tongfang/en/marketing/icons/navigation-icons/document.svg')" target="_blank" data-at-module="faq_list::How to Change PAL to NTSC for 3MP TVI Camera::How-to-Change-PAL-to-NTSC-for-3MP-TVI-Camera.pdf">How-to-Change-PAL-to-NTSC-for-3MP-TVI-Camera.pdf</a>
        </li>
    </ul>
</div>
</li>
<li class="faq-item section">
<div class="topic collapsed at-action" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapsefaq_369117995" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapsefaq_369117995" data-tag="|TURBO HD CAMERA|" data-at-module="faq_list::click::How to Connect External Alarm Output with PIR Camera">How to Connect External Alarm Output with PIR Camera</div>
<div class="content-section collapse" id="collapsefaq_369117995" data-parent="#faqAccordionfaq_container_copy">
    <div class="description hiknow-rte"><p>The PIR camera with O in the model name provides an alarm output interface (EXT ALARM OUTPUT), and an external alarm equipment can be connected to the interface. When you turn on the EXT ALARM OUTPUT and the PIR alarm is triggered, the external alarm device will also be triggered. We recommend that PIR camera and K series DVR be used together to provide more accurate alarm information. </p>
</div>
