<div class="content-section collapse" id="collapsefaq_1974911537" data-parent="#faqAccordionfaq_container_copy">
    <div class="description hiknow-rte"><p>Camera Installation Requirements </p>
<p>1. The height of the camera needs to be in the range of 2.5 m to 6 m. </p>
<p>2. The tilt angle of the camera is recommended to be in the range of 25° to 60°. </p>
<p>3. The best detection area is within 6 m of the horizontal distance from the camera. </p>
</div>
    <ul class="assets-list">
        
        <li>
            <a class="asset at-action" href="https://www.tongfangbms.com/content/dam/tongfang/en/support/how-to/how-to-document/network-cameras/How-to-Configure-Distance-Exception-Function.pdf" style="background-image:url('https://www.tongfangbms.com/content/dam/tongfang/en/marketing/icons/navigation-icons/document.svg')" target="_blank" data-at-module="faq_list::How to Configure Distance Exception Function::How-to-Configure-Distance-Exception-Function.pdf">How-to-Configure-Distance-Exception-Function.pdf</a>
