<div class="content-section collapse" id="collapsefaq_529122543" data-parent="#faqAccordionfaq_container_copy">
    <div class="description hiknow-rte"><p> 1. Make sure VCA Resource Type has been selected with Temperature Measurement option as default.</p>
<p>2. Make sure Display Temperature info option are enabled.</p>
<p>3. Temperature measurement basic settings. Check the checkbox to enable temperature Measurement function.</p>
<p>4. Temperature measurement normal mode</p>
