    <div class="description hiknow-rte"><p>After Hikvision shuts down iVMS-4500 and HiDDNS services, installers who previously used iVMS-4500 and HiDDNS services can add devices to Hik-ProConnect to provide remote operation, maintenance and management services for end users. Devices can be added to Hik-ProConnect through P2P and IP/Domain. This document will introduce them in detail.</p>
